title: Bohdan Smishko
content:
Bohdan Smishko (Ukrainian: Богдан Володимирович Смішко; born 20 August 1978) is a Ukrainian former professional football defender. He is a brother of goalkeeper Roman Smishko.

Smishko started his football career at amateur level playing for FC Dnister Ovidiopol.
